      "searchable_text": "[28. May 2020] Queen Hotfix 12.2"
    },
    {
      "heading": "Mobile Improvements and Fixes",
      "description": null,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "Joystick control improvements",
          "subitems": [
            {
              "text": "Virtual joystick now scales its touch area size based on UI scaling"
            },
            {
              "text": "Moved mount button to the right of the joystick and decreased its size"
            },
            {
              "text": "Enabled \"Double press to attack\" in joystick control settings"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Added option to ignore low-tier resources while gathering using the action button"
        },
        {
          "text": "Added option to disable \"Double-Tap Opens Zoom Mode\""
        },
        {
          "text": "Added on-press tooltips to buff/debuff effects"
        },
        {
          "text": "Adjusted Destiny tracker in HUD to show more entries depending on screen space"
        },
        {
          "text": "Added conditional keyboard shortcut displays for bottom layout spells when mouse present"
        },
        {
          "text": "Tap-control bottom layout now more closely resembles desktop layout"
        },
        {
          "text": "Improved carry capacity indicator readability"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fixed an issue where Marketplace category submenus were offscreen at 100% scaling"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fixed an issue where spell buttons could appear slightly rotated when switching vanity/combat spells and moving spell bar"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fixed an issue where mount button appearance was not updated when pressed"
        }
      ],
      "subsections": [],
      "searchable_text": "Mobile Improvements and Fixes Joystick control improvements Virtual joystick now scales its touch area size based on UI scaling Moved mount button to the right of the joystick and decreased its size Enabled \"Double press to attack\" in joystick control settings Added option to ignore low-tier resources while gathering using the action button Added option to disable \"Double-Tap Opens Zoom Mode\" Added on-press tooltips to buff/debuff effects Adjusted Destiny tracker in HUD to show more entries depending on screen space Added conditional keyboard shortcut displays for bottom layout spells when mouse present Tap-control bottom layout now more closely resembles desktop layout Improved carry capacity indicator readability Fixed an issue where Marketplace category submenus were offscreen at 100% scaling Fixed an issue where spell buttons could appear slightly rotated when switching vanity/combat spells and moving spell bar Fixed an issue where mount button appearance was not updated when pressed"
    },
    {
      "heading": "Mail UI Improvements",
      "description": null,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "Updated timers: expiration timer in read view, received timer in inbox"
        },
        {
          "text": "Bought/sold items now appear in bold"
        },
        {
          "text": "Increased font size in read view"
        },
        {
          "text": "Item icons now clickable in messages"
        },
        {
          "text": "Improved alignment and readability of messages"
        }
      ],
      "subsections": [],
      "searchable_text": "Mail UI Improvements Updated timers: expiration timer in read view, received timer in inbox Bought/sold items now appear in bold Increased font size in read view Item icons now clickable in messages Improved alignment and readability of messages"
    },
    {
      "heading": "Other Changes",
      "description": null,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "Damage from yourself or allies is no longer lethal, and now results only in knockdown"
